Private Bookings & Event Catering
Click Button Below For More Information
Event Information Request Form
Celebrate your wedding in our beautiful beer garden
Hosting Your Event at Motorworks Brewing
Flexible Venue Options & Affordable Fees
Flexible Venue Options & Affordable Fees
Flexible Venue Options & Affordable Fees
Our event venue fees are based on group size/specifics of the event and include setup and cleanup, as well as dedicated servers to ensure your event runs smoothly.  Live music in the beer garden adds to the ambiance, with bands performing Fridays, Saturdays & Sundays
Wedding Ceremonies & Receptions
Flexible Venue Options & Affordable Fees
Flexible Venue Options & Affordable Fees
Motorworks is also a fantastic option for wedding ceremonies and receptions.  Our team works closely with couples to ensure everything is just right for your special event
Exceptional Catering Partnerships
Flexible Venue Options & Affordable Fees
Exceptional Catering Partnerships
We proudly partner with trusted local caterers, including Bluewater Catering, celebrated for their exceptional event catering service, custom menus, and flexibility across styles and budgets. From elegant plated dinners to relaxed buffets, every event is tailored to your vision.
Drink Packages
A Dedicated Team to Support You
Exceptional Catering Partnerships
We offer a variety of beverage packages to suit your special event, from full open bar service to thoughtfully curated selections tailored to your style and budget.
A Dedicated Team to Support You
A Dedicated Team to Support You
A Dedicated Team to Support You
From your first inquiry to the final toast, our team is committed to creating a seamless, memorable experience. We’ll help you customize the space, handle every detail, and ensure your guests feel right at home. Whether you’re planning a wedding, corporate gathering, or milestone celebration, Motorworks Brewing is the perfect backdrop for a special event to remember.
Celebrate With Us!
A Dedicated Team to Support You
A Dedicated Team to Support You
Motorworks Brewing is a fantastic event venue for all types of celebrations, including corporate events, birthday parties, anniversaries, graduation parties, holiday gatherings, baby showers, and so much more. We offer flexible availability throughout the day and work with you to coordinate around any scheduled live music in the beer garden, ensuring the right atmosphere for your special event—whether you’re looking for a lively setting or something more laid-back. Our team is here to help bring your vision to life and ensure your celebration is seamless, fun, and memorable.
